  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/655370/extras/565f0e65f396bd18ef1b21d1c0356f12.poster.avif?t=1770686490\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/655370/extras/565f0e65f396bd18ef1b21d1c0356f12.webm?t=1770686490\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE LAW!!</strong></h2><br>Looks to be a showdown atop a train. This will be your last fight. <br><br>Good luck, Train Bandit.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WHAT IS THIS GAME?</strong></h2><br>Train Bandit is a simple score attack game. The Law will attack you from both sides.<br><br>Your weapon is your keyboard. You'll use those keys to kick the living shit out of the law.<br><br>React quickly by attacking the correct direction. React...or you're dead.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE FEATURES</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Unlock new bandits<br></li><li> Earn Achievements<br></li><li> Become Steam's <i>Most Wanted</i>?<br></li><li> Battle elite officers<br></li><li> Kick the law's ass</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/655370/extras/0b9ebcf43121da22175bd1e222c76a44.poster.avif?t=1770686490\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/655370/extras/0b9ebcf43121da22175bd1e222c76a44.webm?t=1770686490\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/655370/extras/565f0e65f396bd18ef1b21d1c0356f12.poster.avif?t=1770686490\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/655370/extras/565f0e65f396bd18ef1b21d1c0356f12.webm?t=1770686490\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE LAW!!</strong></h2><br>Looks to be a showdown atop a train. This will be your last fight. <br><br>Good luck, Train Bandit.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WHAT IS THIS GAME?</strong></h2><br>Train Bandit is a simple score attack game. The Law will attack you from both sides.<br><br>Your weapon is your keyboard. You'll use those keys to kick the living shit out of the law.<br><br>React quickly by attacking the correct direction. React...or you're dead.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE FEATURES</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Unlock new bandits<br></li><li> Earn Achievements<br></li><li> Become Steam's <i>Most Wanted</i>?<br></li><li> Battle elite officers<br></li><li> Kick the law's ass</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/655370/extras/0b9ebcf43121da22175bd1e222c76a44.poster.avif?t=1770686490\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/655370/extras/0b9ebcf43121da22175bd1e222c76a44.webm?t=1770686490\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
